             was indicted for <rs id="t18220522-38-off201" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220522-38-off201" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220522-38-off201" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
