                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-38-off201 t18220522-38-cd202"></join>, two sheets, value 5 s.; three shirts, value 7 s., and one handkerchief, value 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220522-38-victim351" type="victimName">
                     John Lawrence 
                     Elderton
                  <interp inst="t18220522-38-victim351" type="surname" value="Elderton"></interp>
